                        >BC 307 – 305</origDate>
                  </origin>
                  <provenance>Owned by Pawerem, son of Qjqj in the late 4th century BC.</provenance>
                  <acquisition>Donated to the library by <persName type="person_38033406">John
                        Greville Chester</persName>in 1890</acquisition>
